messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hi, my name is Gioravar and I'm at Plaza and I-35 Travel Plaza because they were trying to kill me.
Okay, is somebody with you now? Are they trying to kill you now?
No, but I know they're going to follow me, because they tried to follow me.
What hotel were you in?
Plaza Inn, room 167.
What's your name?
Gavara.
How old are you?
And are you going to be at this address?
Yes, I am.
Okay, we'll get an officer over there.
Okay, thank you. Bye.
Bye.
9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hi, I'm in the car, because my husband shot someone.
Your husband shot someone?
Yes, I'm in the cop car, and they're trying to kill me. Please help.
What kind of car are you in?
I'm in the cop car.
If you're in the cop car, then you're going to be safe.
No, but they are looking for me. Please help.
What do the people look like who are trying to hurt you?
There are several of them running around.
Where are they?
One of them is near the south side.
Is this the person the officers are looking for?
Yes, I think so.
Can you describe him? Is he black, white, Hispanic?
He's tall with blonde hair.
What is he wearing?
A black shirt with blue lettering and jeans.
Listen, they're saying they have a guy in custody. Is there another one near the cop car?
Yes, there's another one.
Okay, you need to talk into the phone because I can't hear you well.
I'm sorry. I'm just very scared.
I understand, but I need information. Do you see an officer?
No, I don't.
I have about 20 officers right there and you don't see one of them?
Please, just send someone.
Oklahoma 911, what's your emergency?
I was just calling and saw someone running around.
Where are you at?
I'm at Plaza Inn.
Are you the lady that's in the back of the cop car?
Yes.
Okay, do you not see an officer there?
